layout: layouts/element.njk
title: "card-list"
description: "Template-based list rendering with safe data binding. Fetch or inline JSON, bind to templates, and render lists with grid, stack, or reel layouts."
elementName: card-list
category: component
currentPath: /docs/elements/web-components/card-list/
permalink: /docs/elements/web-components/card-list/
